# Keep secrets, local state, and build junk out of the Docker build context. Without this,
# the Dockerfiles' `COPY . .` would bake a local `.env` (dev credentials) into the images and
# the Doris migrate's `--env-file=../../.env` could pick up the wrong connection config.
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
!.env.production.example

.git
.github
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/.turbo
**/*.log

# Public-site build caches (apps/web, apps/docs) — not needed in platform images
**/.astro
**/.wrangler
**/.tanstack

# Local tooling / editor state
.vscode
.idea
.DS_Store
